                            <comment id="13079959" author="slebresne" created="Fri, 5 Aug 2011 13:17:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, I admit I went for lazy no that one, thinking that maybe there was a reason for having getRA returning null. But apparently there is none. Attaching v2 that sets rpcAddress to the right value upfront.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
